Barry Van Dyke -LRB- born July 31 , 1951 -RRB- is an American actor and the second son of actor and entertainer Dick Van Dyke plus he was the stepson of makeup artist Arlene Silver-Van Dyke and nephew of Jerry Van Dyke .
He was best known to audiences as Lieutenant Detective Steve Sloan , a homicide detective and the son of Dr. Mark Sloan -LRB- played by Dick Van Dyke -RRB- on Diagnosis : Murder .
In the show , the characters ' relatives were frequently played by real-life family members .